Interface WaiterCloning

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BarClientProxy, KitchenClientProxy, TableClientProxy

    public interface WaiterCloning
    Barber cloning. It specifies his own attributes. Implementation of a client-server model of type 2 (server replication). Communication is based on a communication channel under the TCP protocol.
